Package: corematch
Type: Package
Title: Corporate Entity Resolution Engine for Research-Grade Company Name Matching
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Yurtsev",
      family = "Uymaz",
      email = "y.uymaz@uea.ac.uk",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: CORE is a modular research software framework for
    corporate entity resolution. It provides reproducible workflows
    for cleaning company names, suffix normalization, alias handling,
    candidate generation, similarity scoring, manual review,
    learning-based decision reuse, and export of reproducible,
    analysis-ready matched datasets.
